the ususal 10% production.
the lead actors were pretty good.  some nice location shots and a

i don't know what (gay)&(straight)male actors have to be afraid of in doing full frontal nudity.  european actors do what is necessary for the story and it shows in the quality of their films.
Sorry but the acting in this movie is horrible. Almost funny as it is so bad. If you want a movie that has some nice looking beefcake then this is it. Other than that it is not worth buying.
